{"tid":179332,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀過廚藝嘅巴絲打入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-03-30T07:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T07:45:39.000Z","uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b2ac5dd7923ea910defc7d8cf987a8d59604ca2","tid":179332,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早幾個月係廚藝學院畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畢業到而家都有keep住炒散。<br />\n由於飲食業 工時太長，<br />\n每日十幾個鐘係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日24小時 返工都冇咗半日 計埋瞓覺<br />\n得幾個鐘係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，私人時間得好少。<br />\n因為工時長嘅問題，所以未必會做飲食業。<br />\n雖然有興趣，但唔係想像中咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n有冇飲食業嘅巴絲打可以分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我仲決定緊讀HD 定 投身社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9110be20d7785c36c436b238e16e5808eb32fa92","tid":179332,"uid":88094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"你係絲定巴？"},{"pid":"09fd8b477ffe35d42878cacf4cdfb32b61855f4a","tid":179332,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係絲定巴？</blockquote><br />\n絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2caaca68780a41e9c46dddc195978efc46a0eb","tid":179332,"uid":99545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"繼續讀啦"},{"pid":"7713ff569f44b4ffdfdbefcc8aa55f8cdf1eae13","tid":179332,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07: